%3Fl%3Dtchinese&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWA3x%2FUg%2Bgbtl8eFt0uNm3qw%3D&h=5ec96b5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://steamcommunity.com/games/221410/announcements/detail/1696055855739350561?l=tchinese</a><br />\n<br />\n目前尚<span style=\"color: red;\">不支援 Linux 的 Windows 遊戲現在能安裝並可直接於 Linux Steam 用戶端中運作</span>，帶原生 Steamworks 與 OpenVR 支援，更加完整。<br />\n<br />\nDirectX11 與 12 實作現在以 Vulkan 為基礎，改善了遊戲相容性並減少效能影響。<br />\n<br />\n改善全螢幕支援：可配合選定的螢幕完美調整全螢幕遊戲，不干擾原生螢幕解析度，無需使用虛擬桌面。<br />\n<br />\n改善遊戲控制器支援：遊戲會自動辨識所有 Steam 支援的控制器。即買即用的盒裝控制器相容性提升，甚至可能比原版遊戲的支援更加優秀。<br />\n<br />\n多執行緒遊戲之效能相較一般的 Wine 大幅提升。"},{"pid":"f0b072cd3c79471dcbfbe1681dde352e53f442a8","tid":1173517,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1a5fa975db4e99434912dfc8975553b2459487f","tid":1173517,"uid":123497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9dcdadab83904e103106c16c1b4ddcf9bb8c3a6","tid":1173517,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:49:37.000Z","msg":"唔可以，因為我有打機成癮症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：學生時期試過一段時間只用linux，程式方面還可以，大部分常用app都有linux版，但九成九game都無linux版，所以頂唔順放棄佐，至於雙修，既然點都要裝window，又點叫完全取代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:53:35.000Z","msg":"依家有dxvk同埋d9vk好少game玩唔到其實"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:05:09.000Z","msg":"online games 咪玩唔到"},{"pid":"7f46b3470af44bfad39c054f38c7ff78f4599bb7","tid":1173517,"uid":28563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1d933b486beff4c08b127f309b575709c21ce3c1","tid":1173517,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T07:36:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:10:44.000Z","msg":"考古2004年linux?"},{"pid":"40059a276bf279ac2cdbfe696a4de77b3edfe2e0","tid":1173517,"uid":131120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:13:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91597c0386a4b82405b3ca0c46e12aa7a755b854","tid":